divs: Sighting DetailsThis is not the first time i have noticed a ufo but was amazed at this encounter. I had come home from a local bar hanging out with some friends around 2:30 started watching a movie when i got in and when it was over headed twords my bedroom to go lay down. Thats when i noticed a very bright light moving across the sky very fast and then it just shot upward and vanished. It was just above 3rd and south st in philadelphia. I checked the news and even youtube to see if anyone had witnessed what i saw But there were no reports...
Summary: ufo spotted over center city philadelphia (south street) which seem to be flying west and suddenly just blasted up and out of sight.
